{"tid":615253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國鐵路工會罷工三個月　抗議總統推行改革 450萬名鐵路乘客受影響","createTime":"2018-04-03T08:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T06:40:08.000Z","uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03834a2443696a833c65fb835f2107c32feefb78","tid":615253,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"法國鐵路工會發動罷工，抗議總統馬克龍推行的改革。工業行動將持續三個月，預計會有450萬名鐵路乘客受影響。 在當地星期二，八班高速鐵路中，只有一班預計能夠行駛。而前往倫敦及布魯塞爾的歐洲之星列車，有四分之三成行。但前往西班牙、意大利及瑞士的列車就取消。 馬克龍認為，法國鐵路行業，相對其他歐洲國家的成本高三成，需要於2020年歐盟國家開放鐵路競爭巿場前，作出改革。 工會指馬克龍的行為將破壞公共鐵路行業，又擔心政府會將全資由政府擁有的鐵路變為私人公司。"},{"pid":"c40dd3cd5cfa32bc3937e2685dc32f98efe23fb5","tid":615253,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"香港狗巴紀錄 罷工一晚 (未過夜)"},{"pid":"997944b6bbc9ec344f6439e993b4a7e6847e5a6e","tid":615253,"uid":45285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"諗起D的士佬罷駛&hellip;唔係改變又怕被人淘汰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e459818223e9638c1267fd95fd2c3ffaa322517","tid":615253,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"香港人=佛系市民"},{"pid":"d262dc75ffb0613bbc585ccfeb90b1b052b7e5a6","tid":615253,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"香港人: 你有訴求我唔阻你呀 但你唔好阻住我搵食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391de26d35078255d68c55407c4b3feb481c6dc0","tid":615253,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6241841ff77e282b934a7630418ed3cec52c278","tid":615253,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e0855ff58c63388456c177411ab9384b9285f1","tid":6152